.@DarrenSarll: "I am heartbroken for @AMarriott10. We took our time with him but as soon as you saw him, you knew. I wish he was with us."
.@DarrenSarll: "I thought Pritchard was outstanding against us earlier in the season. When the chance came to get him, it was a no brainer."
@DarrenSarll: "That little bit of extra support in coaching and management that Glenn will bring will be invaluable."
.@DarrenSarll: "Feedback is always something I have been willing to take on and I welcome any help the football club can get."
